title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 15 2022
description:
Kerry and Granholm: No need to drill, just buy an expensive electric car. Total lie: Dems claim inflation caused by obstruction of Biden agenda. CNN pollster: Biden is doing worse than Jimmy Carter. Joe Scarborough and the Morning Joe crew echo C&B on Manchin saving the Democrats by killing Build Back Better. DeSantis' all-time response to Elon Musk's support. Hispanic caller from Texas tells C&B why Hispanics are switching to the GOP.
